{"clause_group_id":"21H","contribution_mode_code":"B","external_source_file_dependency":"NO","line_id":"2ZU","normalized_text":"天府躔夫妻宫，称为善曜，纵使会星曜恶，一般亦仅主生离，不主死别。","normalized_text_sha256":"bcb7fc719731a0d2987cab515cf348591003447da32988bfa743a1ac63e2daac","raw_text":"天府躔夫妻宫，称为善曜，纵使会星曜恶，一般亦仅主生离，不主死别。","raw_text_sha256":"bcb7fc719731a0d2987cab515cf348591003447da32988bfa743a1ac63e2daac","runtime_atom_text_id":"S07-RAT-39D","runtime_read_status":"PASS","section_id":"PX","source_atom_id":"39D"}
